x_2 = 2  - \frac 1 {x_n} \gt 2 - 1 = 1
x_2 = 2  - \frac 1 {x_2} = \dfrac{2x_2 - 1}{x_2} = 1 + \dfrac{x_2 -1}{x_2} \lt 1 + x_2 - 1 = x_2
1 \lt x_2 \lt x_1
