 x_{n + 2} = 2 - \frac{1}{x_{n+ 1} } = \frac{2x_{n + 1} - 1}{x_{n + 1}} = 1 + \frac{x_{n + 1} - 1}{x_{n + 1}} \lt 1 + x_{n + 1} - 1 = x_{n + 1} 
 1 \lt x_{n + 2} \lt x_{n + 1} 
